No fewer than nine soldiers of Operation Lafiya Dole were reportedly killed, while 20 others could not be accounted for after a battle with insurgents in Gudumbali town of Borno State. This followed a fierce battle between the troops and Boko Haram insurgents who were said to have planned a massive attack in the axis. Channels Television gathered that the soldiers were ambushed by the terrorists in a village called Granda, engaging them overnight from Monday until the early hours of Tuesday. <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1254008" src="https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=300%2C169&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="300" height="169" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=300%2C169&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=1024%2C576&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=58%2C33&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=260%2C146&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=200%2C112&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?resize=560%2C315&amp;ssl=1 560w, https://i1.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0012.jpg?w=1080&amp;ssl=1 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1254009" src="https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG-20190913-WA0011.jpg?resize=300%2C169&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="300" height="169" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/cdn.vanguardngr.com/wp-co